blog.title: BTS Art and Writing Prompts
blog.description: A blog for prompts, ideas and sources of inspiration to help my fellow ARMY in contributing to Fandom! Please see #introduction and #rules for full details on using my posts.

body:
Ocean’s 7 Au

Part 4/7

Jungkook the pickpocket. He’s fast, light on his feet, and has a face so innocent that nobody suspects him. On the very rare occasion that he does get noticed, he’s up and out of there before anyone can even reach for their phone (usually to discover that he’s stolen it). His Parkour skills are ridiculous and sometimes verge on the unnecessary - there’s no such thing as a stealthy get away in his book.

He doesn’t even care that much about the money. He just does it for the thrill of knowing he’s that little bit better than everyone else.

“You’re RM? The RM? Oh my god, I’m going to die - the answer is yes, whatever it is I’ll do it!”

And Jimin couldn’t remember why they’re talking about that, but he remembered every word, every emotion he felt that night, how he wanted to kiss Namjoon so bad. How he wanted to just throw everything away and tell Namjoon he knew what he meant.
